entor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/www.airbnb.com\/rooms\/31305842\/reviews?source_impression_id=p3_1746730943_P3LCqBHHof0TzwN6\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"th-linea icon th-linea icon-arrows-slim-right\"><\/i>\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">view all reviews on airbnb <\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f84a855 elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-testimonial-slider\" data-id=\"f84a855\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;items&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:3,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;items_tablet&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:1,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;items_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:1,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]}}\" data-widget_type=\"eael-testimonial-slider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n        <div class=\"swiper-container-wrap eael-arrow-box swiper-container-wrap-dots-outside eael-testimonial-slider middle-style\" id=\"eael-testimonial-f84a855\">\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"swiper swiper-8 eael-testimonial-slider-main swiper-container-f84a855 eael-marquee-carousel\" data-pagination=\".swiper-pagination-f84a855\" data-arrow-next=\".swiper-button-next-f84a855\" data-arrow-prev=\".swiper-button-prev-f84a855\" data-items=\"3\" data-items-tablet=\"1\" data-items-mobile=\"1\" data-margin=\"10\" data-effect=\"slide\" data-speed=\"7403\" data-loop=\"1\" data-grab-cursor=\"1\" data-arrows=\"1\" data-dots=\"1\" data-autoplay_speed=\"0.001\">\n\n                <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-testimonial-item clearfix swiper-slide  eael-testimonial-align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-testimonial-item-inner clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-testimonial-content rating-five\" style=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"eael-testimonial-quote\"><\/span><div class=\"eael-testimonial-text eael-testimonial-text-excerpt\">First time staying at Lantana and will stay again. The property was very comfortable and...<button class=\"eael-testimonial-read-more-btn\">Read More<\/button><\/div><div class=\"eael-testimonial-text eael-testimonial-text-full-text\"><p>First time staying at Lantana and will stay again. The property was very comfortable and was pretty well stocked. Maisha was very responsive and took care of any needs. The balcony is the highlight of the property. The condo is positioned where you have a nice view and breezy. The property position is out of the afternoon sun. The location is centrally located and easy access to the highway, Holetown and Speightstown. <br \/>I didn\u2019t find the stairs challenging, but my travel partner did for the first few days. The 3rd floor has its benefits with high ceilings. The only thing I would change is the washer\/dryer combo. The \u201cdryer\u201d is the spin cycle. A mention or picture of the unit would have changed my expectations. But once I looked up the operating instructions, it was no problem.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t        <div class=\"eael-testimonial-image\">\n\t\t\t            <figure>\n                <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/forrentbarbados.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/Airbnb-Logo-2014-scaled.png\" alt=\"\">\n            <\/figure>\n        <\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"middle-style-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t        <ul class=\"testimonial-star-rating\">\n            <li><i class=\"fa fa-star\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/li>\n            <li><i class=\"fa fa-star\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/li>\n            <li><i class=\"fa fa-star\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/li>\n            <li><i class=\"fa fa-star\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/li>\n            <li><i class=\"fa fa-star\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i><\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n\t\t        <p class=\"eael-testimonial-user\"  style=\"display: block; float: none;\" >Janet<\/p>\n        <p class=\"eael-testimonial-user-company\">January 2023 \u00b7 Stayed over a week<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-testimonial-item clearfix swiper-slide  eael-testimonial-align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-testimonial-item-inner clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"eael-testimonial-content rating-five\" style=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"eael-testimonial-quote\"><\/span><div class=\"eael-testimonial-text eael-testimonial-text-excerpt\">Maisha place was exceptional! She was quick to respond with anything I asked. I had...<button class=\"eael-testimonial-read-more-btn\">Read More<\/button><\/div><div class=\"eael-testimonial-text eael-testimonial-text-full-text\"><p>Maisha place was exceptional! She was quick to respond with anything I asked. I had a last minute booking and she made sure the condo was clean and available for when I came. There were plenty of recommendations on places to go. Supermarket, restaurants was near. Local bus was steps away along with the beach. I would definitely recommend anyone to stay and if looking forward on booking with Maisha again on my next stay.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t        <div class=\"eael-testimonial-image\">\n\t\t\t            <figure>\n                <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/forrentbarbados.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/Airbnb-Logo-2014-scaled.png\" alt=\"\">\n            <\/figure>\n        <\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"middle-style-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\